    page5: "Now let's solve 9 - 2 on a number line. Step 1: Put your finger on 9. Step 2: Hop backward 2 times: to 8, 7. Step 3: You land on 7, so 9 - 2 = 7.",
    page6: "A helpful trick: always hop to the LEFT for subtraction — the opposite direction from addition, which hops right.",
